[Building the Demo]

Method 1:

  Execute M.BAT on each subdirectory.
  The corresponding sample is created.

Method 2:

  Execute mkall?.bat (specify h or g for ?) in the segasmp\sgl
  directory.
  All samples are created.

[Startup Instructions]

Star up the debugger and target and initialize the target.
Halt the target and then load the executable file from 0x06010000.

Execute the program from the address above.

